law.history: Repealed 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 166, sec. 16, effective July 15, 2010. -- Created 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 496, sec. 12, effective April 10, 1998.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Discontinuance of operation of Kentucky Health Purchasing Alliance -- Executive director to terminate alliance activities by June 30, 1999.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/2010). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 166 prevails over its amendment in 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24.
